    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps, the assessment team accepted the package based on the primary hemolysis validation result and Monte Carlo UQ convergence evidence. The intermediate shear-stress distribution validation result (intermediate-orphan) was included in scope but its provenance was not fully traced. All 13 factors were reviewed; 7 assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels and 6 factors remain as epistemic gaps. Accepted conditionally pending resolution of open epistemic gaps in subsequent submissions.",
